{
  "logNo": "110188645148",
  "title": "춘천 애니메이션박물관, 로봇체험관",
  "addDate": "2014. 4. 8.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110188645148",
  "html_size": 201978,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110188645148\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110188645148\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p>살짝 내린 봄비가 미세먼지를 없애준 주말.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>친구네 가족들과 춘천 여행을 다녀왔습니다.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>애들이 얼추 비슷한 나이대에 몰려있어서 오전에 애니메이션 박물관을 가기로 합니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" />&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/36f8337cab1cfbaf.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_253/isuhani_1396933104316bwV43_JPEG/IMG_7938.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/36f8337cab1cfbaf.jpg\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>구름빵이 여전히 인기인가 보네요. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>애니메이션박물관 간판에 구름빵이 똭~!!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>구름빵 작가분이 저희 애들 유치원 친구 어머니라는 와이프의 설명에</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>시큰둥한 표정 지어주고 ^^</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Go!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/16ca6f4767a4238b.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_177/isuhani_1396933104933i5JE8_JPEG/IMG_7943.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/16ca6f4767a4238b.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>표를 끊고, </p><p>로봇 공연이 곧 있을 예정이라는 안내멘트에따라 </p><p>우선 로봇체험관 먼저 가기로 합니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>친구와 언니가 함께하니</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>엄마 아빠의 손이 덜가서 너~무 좋네요.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_125/isuhani_13969331052313rONE_JPEG/IMG_7944.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_125/isuhani_13969331052313rONE_JPEG/IMG_7944.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_125/isuhani_13969331052313rONE_JPEG/IMG_7944.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>로봇 체험관 건물입니다. 광장도 넓고 좋네요. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_158/isuhani_1396933105371eonIN_JPEG/IMG_7948.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_158/isuhani_1396933105371eonIN_JPEG/IMG_7948.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_158/isuhani_1396933105371eonIN_JPEG/IMG_7948.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>입구에서 맞아주는 로봇에 흥분시작!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_187/isuhani_1396933105865R5Iom_JPEG/IMG_7951.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_187/isuhani_1396933105865R5Iom_JPEG/IMG_7951.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_187/isuhani_1396933105865R5Iom_JPEG/IMG_7951.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>체험관에 들어가니 이런 로봇들이 반겨주네요. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>어두워서 사진이 안나와요 </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bf31ac38764f0dc6.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 825px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_100/isuhani_1396933105697AUo8m_JPEG/IMG_7949.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bf31ac38764f0dc6.jpg\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>진지하게 구경하는 아이들.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b46c1ce637fc74d5.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_102/isuhani_1396933106031lh3tP_JPEG/IMG_7952.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b46c1ce637fc74d5.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>다음 코스로 넘어가니 과학상자를 활용해서 만든</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>공 옮기는 로봇. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>아들이 좀 더 크면 과학상자 세트를 사줘야겠어요. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>제가 어릴적에도 과학상자 하나면 몇날 몇일을 엉덩이 붙이고 놀았었던 기억이 나네요.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3c3e1ddef2ebe346.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 825px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_249/isuhani_1396933106251Sh17y_JPEG/IMG_7953.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3c3e1ddef2ebe346.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>갑자기 매우 즐겁운 표정. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>뭔데?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8efecd274772c73f.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 825px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_292/isuhani_1396933106458OjDbx_JPEG/IMG_7954.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8efecd274772c73f.jpg\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>화면에 표시된대로 몸을 움직이면 아이언맨처럼 갑옷이 입혀지는 체험이네요.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>아이언맨과 어벤져스에 빠져있는 아들은 황홀경~~~ </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_211/isuhani_1396933696030zXz0g_JPEG/IMG_7956.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_211/isuhani_1396933696030zXz0g_JPEG/IMG_7956.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_211/isuhani_1396933696030zXz0g_JPEG/IMG_7956.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>어른들이 좋아할만한 과거의 로봇 캐릭터들.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>마징가 Z 와 태권V 등등.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>역시나 애들은 크게 관심이 없어요~~</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_142/isuhani_1396933696477wiAAV_JPEG/IMG_7958.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_142/isuhani_1396933696477wiAAV_JPEG/IMG_7958.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_142/isuhani_1396933696477wiAAV_JPEG/IMG_7958.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>로봇 공연이 시작된다고 해서 공연장으로 들어갑니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>공연을 기다리는 5분이 애들에겐 긴~ 시간이겠죠?</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_4/isuhani_1396933697025aRu5j_JPEG/IMG_7963.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_4/isuhani_1396933697025aRu5j_JPEG/IMG_7963.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_4/isuhani_1396933697025aRu5j_JPEG/IMG_7963.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>구름빵 가족이 오프닝을 합니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>인형같지만, 로봇이라서 움직입니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_51/isuhani_1396933696646GOKv4_JPEG/IMG_7961.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_51/isuhani_1396933696646GOKv4_JPEG/IMG_7961.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_51/isuhani_1396933696646GOKv4_JPEG/IMG_7961.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>춤을 추는 로봇들. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>중심 잡고 팔다리 움직이는거 보니 신기하네요.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>어릴적 로봇만드는 과학자가 될거라고 장래희망을 말하고 다녔었는데, </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>내가 아닌 다른 사람들이 로봇을 만들고 있군요.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_89/isuhani_1396933696791MLSiL_JPEG/IMG_7962.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_89/isuhani_1396933696791MLSiL_JPEG/IMG_7962.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_89/isuhani_1396933696791MLSiL_JPEG/IMG_7962.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>마리.</p><p>음악을 연주하는 로봇입니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>공연은 길지 않게 끝났는데, 애들 몰입도가 좋더군요. 신나는 음악과 흥겨운 로봇 율동.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f6ff479a7781efc0.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_21/isuhani_1396933697192nCFRd_JPEG/IMG_7968.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f6ff479a7781efc0.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>애들이 아주~ 좋아했던 체험이</p><p>로봇 축구입니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>로봇 공연에서 춤을 추던 로봇과 같은 걸로 추정(?) 되는 로봇들이 축구장에서 서있으면</p><p>아이들이 리모콘으로 조종합니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>아들녀석과&nbsp; 친구의 딸이 한 팀이 되고,</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c523875d7a8bd920.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_234/isuhani_1396933697341H33g8_JPEG/IMG_7972.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c523875d7a8bd920.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>또다른 친구들의 아들과 딸이 한 팀이 됩니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/cf5ad88f3901e23a.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_149/isuhani_1396933697466UXMy5_JPEG/IMG_7973.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/cf5ad88f3901e23a.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>내가 조종하는대로 로봇이 움직이는게 마냥 신기하고 재밌나봅니다.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>로봇 축구시합이긴 하지만, 니편 내편도 의미없고 </p><p>그냥 잠깐 로봇을 리모콘으로 조종해봤다는 정도라고 생각하시면 됩니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4233c4076f0745d1.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_198/isuhani_1396933697598zXlBb_JPEG/IMG_7975.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4233c4076f0745d1.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>이것도 일종의 로봇축구 게임.</p><p>아들녀석과 친구의 아들이 한 팀.</p><p>맞은 편엔 어른 둘.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>조작하는게 쉽지 않더군요.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/735626975b0b4841.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 825px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_144/isuhani_1396933697759sSYE4_JPEG/IMG_7980.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/735626975b0b4841.jpg\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>이번엔 로봇 권투시합.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>친구의 아들이 뭔가 뜻대로 안되는지 인상을 쓰고 있네요 ^^</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/14e23f92ee65c1d3.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 825px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_231/isuhani_1396938559585F7zAR_JPEG/IMG_7983.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/14e23f92ee65c1d3.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>아이들 중 가장 언니였던 아이는</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>사뭇 진지한 표정으로 로봇 권투시합을 치르고 있네요</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>애들이 로봇체험관에 계속 있겠다는걸 </p><p>억지로 끌고 나갑니다. </p><p>(어른들은 이미 체력이 소진되기 시작 ㅎ)</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>바로 옆 건물 애니메이션 박물관으로 들어갑니다. </p><p>곧 점심시간이라서 후다닥 보고 나오기로 친구들끼리 합의하고 </p><p>입장!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_236/isuhani_1396938681229pCcOt_JPEG/IMG_7984.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_236/isuhani_1396938681229pCcOt_JPEG/IMG_7984.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_236/isuhani_1396938681229pCcOt_JPEG/IMG_7984.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>입구에는 애니메이터의 작업광경을 형상화해뒀더군요. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>애니메이션을 보는 우리는 즐겁지만</p><p>애니메이션을 그리는 애니메이터들은 고생이 이만저만 아니겠죠 ㅜ.ㅠ</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_293/isuhani_1396938681394xVima_JPEG/IMG_7985.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_293/isuhani_1396938681394xVima_JPEG/IMG_7985.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_293/isuhani_1396938681394xVima_JPEG/IMG_7985.JPG?type=w3\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>애니메이션 박물관으로의 여행을 시작합니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/583128773fc65028.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_27/isuhani_1396938559840kv8jE_JPEG/IMG_7987.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/583128773fc65028.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>영사기, 사진기, 복사기, 등등</p><p>애니메이션을 만들기 위한 기계들이 주욱~ 전시되어 있습니다. </p><p>주로 예전 기계들이고</p><p>초창기 애니메이션을 만들던 방식들도 애들이 호기심 갖고 관람할 수 있게 </p><p>잘 만들어 놨네요</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_21/isuhani_13969385600257Qb77_JPEG/IMG_7988.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_21/isuhani_13969385600257Qb77_JPEG/IMG_7988.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_21/isuhani_13969385600257Qb77_JPEG/IMG_7988.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>영화관도 있고, </p><p>2층 도 있고.. </p><p>규모가 제법입니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>로봇체험관에서 기운을 소진한 어른들은 </p><p>입구에서부터 전의를 상실 ㅎㅎ</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f62cba45f520a513.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_75/isuhani_1396938560248jGPpp_JPEG/IMG_7993.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f62cba45f520a513.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>어른들은 이름도 모르는 캐릭터. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>애들은 잘 알더군요. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>애들과 호흡을 맞추려면 애들이 좋아하는 것들에 대한 공부(!!!)가 필요하겠어요</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_4/isuhani_1396938560406ORa9v_JPEG/IMG_7995.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_4/isuhani_1396938560406ORa9v_JPEG/IMG_7995.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_4/isuhani_1396938560406ORa9v_JPEG/IMG_7995.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>이쁜 캐릭터는 여자아이들이 관심집중!!!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_123/isuhani_1396938560798EAA0p_JPEG/IMG_7996.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_123/isuhani_1396938560798EAA0p_JPEG/IMG_7996.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_123/isuhani_1396938560798EAA0p_JPEG/IMG_7996.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>만화영화에 푹 빠진 남자 아이들</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d9f551086975e1d4.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_116/isuhani_1396938561011WyjaL_JPEG/IMG_8000.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d9f551086975e1d4.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>아빠에게도 잘 안하는 </p><p>사랑해 포옹을.... </p><p>ㅜ.ㅠ</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/aea44a1acc0aacad.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 825px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_284/isuhani_1396938561262kYgrl_JPEG/IMG_8002.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/aea44a1acc0aacad.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>시간을 여유있게 잡고 </p><p>와야겠더군요. </p><p>그래야 구석구석 충분 보고, 만지고 감상 할 수 있을 것 같아요.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1d89252bd9709ac2.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 825px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_250/isuhani_1396938589285rvjVA_JPEG/IMG_8010.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1d89252bd9709ac2.jpg\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>아빠의 마음은 급합니다. </p><p>밖에서 친구들이 나오라고 계속 연락오고,</p><p>안에서는 아들 딸이 해볼거 다 해보고 싶다고 아우성이고.</p><p>아이구야.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_197/isuhani_1396938561601zUdbJ_JPEG/IMG_8007.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_197/isuhani_1396938561601zUdbJ_JPEG/IMG_8007.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140408_197/isuhani_1396938561601zUdbJ_JPEG/IMG_8007.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p>애니메이션 캐릭터들과 함께하는</p><p>다양한 체험거리들. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>아주 그냥... </p><p>신났어요.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8652a1dfd8801d3d.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140408_214/isuhani_1396938561908UTFk1_JPEG/IMG_8011.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C14B1C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8652a1dfd8801d3d.jpg\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>겨우 데리고 나오는데</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>딸이.. 입구에 있는 판넬을 배경으로 사진찍어달라고 ^^</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>이렇게.</p><p>춘천 애니메이션박물관과 로봇체험관을 후다닥 구경하고 </p><p>우리는 밥 먹으러 갔답니다.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
